♪You don't know my heart♪

113
00:09:12,090 --> 00:09:15,490
♪Dreams shattered, with no one to speak♪

114
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:19,210
♪I fear the most that you leave me♪

115
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,480
♪With what kind of gaze♪

116
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,240
♪What kind of identity♪

117
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:26,510
♪Should I wait
for your glance and a kiss?♪

118
00:09:26,950 --> 00:09:28,710
♪No matter how far♪

119
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:30,650
♪No matter how many lifetimes♪

120
00:09:30,650 --> 00:09:33,490
♪I long to see your love, no parting♪

121
