♪I just want to be with you♪

122
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:40,330
♪Roaming the mortal world together♪

123
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:43,890
♪Even if I have to go♪

124
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:47,590
♪Through several reincarnations♪

125
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:51,320
♪I just want to be with you♪

126
00:09:51,730 --> 00:09:56,140
♪Under the falling stars♪

127
